Under normal circumstances your gecko will only need 3 to 5 feedings per week. How much should I offer my gecko per feeding? It depends on the age of your gecko. Most Juveniles should receive about 1/16th of an ounce or a dime size portion. Subadults should receive 1/8th of an ounce or a nickel sized portion. An adult should receive a quarter to about a half ounce portion. Why shouldn't I freeze the diet to help it last longer? The ice crystals that form during the freezing process can potentially damage the cell walls of the plant ingredient contents and reduce the overall nutritional value of the diet. Why does the unrefrigerated prepared feed expire after a day? The prepared feed can be compared to a fruit smoothie. A fruit smoothie sitting in a humid tropical environment like a gecko terrarium will not last as long as it would while refrigerated.

Blade are more durable after heat treating.   Welding The last step is welding the blade after cutting it to correct size, the welding joint looks much perfect after welding it on high quality imported welding machine, blade life could improve a lot.   Cold Rolling   Milling   Heat Treatment   Welding Blade Teeth Selection Advice and Welding Joint Comparison   How to Improve Life Blade installation is the first step, make sure teeth is shown outside the guide, and blade strip is clamped tightly inside the guide.Teeth direction should be the same with the direction of wheel rotation, twist the blade from inside to outside if teeth direction is opposite.Running-in is required when blade cuts metal for the first time. It's important for blade life. During running-in, cutting speed should be 1/3 of normal speed, feed should be 1/4 of normal feed. Usually, after the blade cuts the first several pieces, like 5-10 pieces, adjust cutting speed and feed gradually to normal speed according relative parameters and your metal.Blade tension will be different for differnt wide blades, as time goes on, blade tension will be reduced by the bandsaw and blade stretch, make sure the blade is correct tension, our recommended blade tension is 300N/mm2.Coolant will be useful to cool and lubricate blade and teeth during cutting, better coolant could avoid overheat on the teeth of the blade, and reduce friction between the blade and the metal you cut.Teeth selection is also important, here are our experience: big variable teeths (like 3/4TPI, 4/6TPI, 5/8TPI) are for cutting ferrous solid rod with big diameter;big constant teeth (like 6TPI) is for cutting ferrous solid rod with small diameter;big variable teeth (like 6/10TPI) is for cutting aluminum, copper, brass etc and other non-ferrous metal;middle variable teeths (like 8/12TPI, 10/14TPI) are for ferrous thick tubing, profile, sheet, plate etc;small constant teeth (14TPI) is for general purpose;small variable teeths (like 12/16TPI, 14/18TPI) is for ferrous thin tubing, sheet, plate, profile etc;small constant teeth (24TPI) is for ferrous thin tubing, plate, sheet etc, don't cut non-ferrous metal, like aluminum etc.       Welding Joint We weld blades with high performance welding machine to make sure welding joint looks perfect. Teeth Direction Default teeth direction is rightward, if you want leftward direction, please twist the blade from inside to outside. Original Package Brand new with original package for this blade with tips behind blade pacakge to help customers.         Metalworking Type Bi-metal blade is designed for metalworking, ideal for metalworking craftman, blacksmith, mechanic etc. Compatibility Accurate length with high performance, compatible with most bandsaws with more choices on teeth pitch. Ideal DIY Tools Bi-metal type, M42 grade, 8% cobalt with 2% tungsten, much more fatigue resistant and durable on metal. Blade Life Spring steel backer strengthens blade life, hardened edges to cut metal straightly with ease, blade works with high performance.

title: 2" NPSH Heavy-Duty Industrial Fire Hose Nozzle with 2 x Aluminum 2 inch Camlock Fittings Couplings Fire Equipment Constant Flow Fog Nozzle
description: ◆Thermoplastic 2" NPSH nozzle attached to 2x 2" NPSH aluminum female camlock◆Maximum operating pressure - 100psi. Approximate gallons per minute (GPM) - 60. Approximate distance - 70 feet◆NH / NST: The most common thread type in use by fire departments today is NST or National Standard Thread. NST also goes by the initials NH or National Hose. It can even be referred to as NHT or National Hose Thread. But NST or NH is more common these days. NH = NST.◆NPSH: National Pipe Straight Hose (NPSH) or Iron Pipe Thread (IPT) has the same threads per inch (TPI) as National Pipe Tapered (NPT) but the thread does not taper. NPSH is a straight thread and seals by a gasket in the female coupling which allows for a swivel, just like NH / NST, which make both ideal for hose couplings. Warning - It will NOT thread into a female NPT pipe. For example, a male NPSH coupling will NOT thread into a female metal or pvc pipe.◆NPT: National Pipe Tapered is common in plumbing and some industrial uses. Sometimes referred to as pipe thread because PVC pipe and schedule 40 pipe are typically threaded in NPT. As its name implies this is a tapered thread so that the outside diameter of the male (ODM) gets smaller towards the end of the fitting and the inside diameter of the female narrows with depth. As the two fittings are threaded together the opposite tapers force thread friction and makes the seal without the use of a gasket.

title: Kate Naturals Mineral Oil for Wood Cutting Board Oil, Butcher Block, and Knife. Food Grade Mineral Oil for Wooden Cutting Board (8oz, Food Safe Oil)
description: Kate Naturals Mineral Oil helps to protect and condition wooden cutting boards, bamboo boards, and butcher blocks. Mineral Oil can also polish marble and soapstone countertops, or clean wooden and stainless steel utensils. Easy Cutting Board Maintenance Mineral Oil protects and conditions wooden cutting boards, bamboo cutting boards, and butcher blocks to help increase its longevity. It works its way into the board and hydrates it, which helps prevent it from drying out and cracking over time. Once applied, it also acts as a barrier against additional moisture that can make its way into the board, which can cause warping. Apply Mineral Oil to your cutting boards each month, or every 2-3 weeks if the cutting board is used daily and frequently.     Protect Wood, Stainless Steel Kitchenware, and Appliances This smooth mineral oil also helps to protect steel blades from rust, including your favorite kitchen knives. You can also use this fantastic mineral oil to clean copper pots, your stainless steel stove, and your fridge. This amazing mineral oil is a completely food-safe way to protect wooden surfaces, with a food-grade formula that’s carefully crafted to protect woods, from cutting boards to wooden spoons to butcher blocks and more. Extend Life of Appliances Our Cutting Board Mineral Oil is perfectly packaged in a bottle and ready to use in any professional or home kitchen. Add a small amount to a damp cloth before gently rubbing it into wooden surfaces in a smooth circular motion. Use a quarter-sized amount to clean and treat stainless steel appliances, such as your fridge, stove, or microwave. Pair this mineral oil with a lightweight cloth to clean and treat copper bowls, stainless steel blades, and more while also providing protection from rust.     About Us Our facility is located in California. We comply with the highest manufacturing standards to ensure that all of our products are top quality. title: Epoxy Putty, 120g 2 Part Fast Repair Epoxy Glue, Pool Repair Putty, Metal, Plastic, Wood, Glass, Ceramic Crack Filler, Heat Resistant and Waterproof (Grey)
description: Manual two-part mix epoxy putty shows great plasticity before curing, hardens like steel after curing, perfect for fixing metal, hard plastic, stone etc. This exhaust repair kit offers more possibilities for functional repairs you can think of.     Application 1. Clean the area to be repaired to avoid impurities and grease. 2. Put on the attached gloves and align the white and dark gray epoxy putty horizontally. 3. Use the attached scraper to mix in a 1:1 ratio. 4. Knead the same amount until the epoxy adhesive turn to light gray. 5. Apply the light gray mixture to the area you want to repair and press the epoxy filler properly to keep it firm. 6. After 24 hours, the plastic putty solidifies and becomes hard, which can be processed, painted, knocked, and drilled. All Purpose Epoxy Putty 1x white epoxy putty（60g）1x dark grey epoxy putty（60g）1x scraper2x gloves Notice Keep metal adhesive away from children. Store metal putty in a dry place. For external use only. Wet your hands before use (When operating without gloves) to avoid staining. Wash your hands with soap after complete.

title: Alessi MDL02/1 B Pulcina Stove Top Espresso 1 Cup Coffee Maker in Aluminum Casting Handle And Knob in Pa, Black
description: The stove top espresso coffee maker "Pulcina", designed by Michele de Lucchi is the product of intense research into the optimization of the shape of the coffee pot in order to improve and enhance the organoleptic properties of coffee. Thanks to the internal shape of its special heater, "Pulcina" automatically stops filtering the coffee at the right moment. This interruption helps to eliminate the eruption phase, the final filtering stage that generates a burnt and bitter aftertaste, ensuring that only the finest qualities of the coffee are preserved and enhancing its full-bodied and rounded aroma. The spout is quite pronounced. Its typical 'V' shape, reminiscent of a baby chick's beak, is specially designed to perfectly cut drops when pouring. Practical and functional, making coffee with the "Pulcina" is just like making it with a traditional coffee pot.

title: Full Moon All Natural Human Grade Dog Treats, Essential Beef Savory Sticks, 22 Ounce, 1.375 Pound (Pack of 1)
description: We believe dogs deserve food that is just as good (dare we say better?) as our own. This commitment drives our choices, from how we raise our animals, to the ingredients we choose, to the kitchens we use. You’ll notice the difference the second you open a bag of our natural dog treats. Our Full Moon treats are made with love in the USA. We work exclusively with the trusted family farmers and ranchers we’ve been in business with for years, ensuring that animals are raised to the highest ethical standards. Every bite begins with USDA-approved, human-grade meat— cooked in gleaming kitchens using only 100% natural ingredients—and ends with a satisfied pup. Each of our healthy snacks, like Full Moon Essential Beef Sticks, are free of artificial preservatives, colors, or flavors and full of things dogs love. Glycerin and fillers like corn, wheat, and soy have no place in our recipes. In other words, we only use simple, natural ingredients you’d find in a grocery store and likely eat yourself, like free range beef, cassava root, and rosemary. Unlike most pet food, we slow cook our treats in small batches using time honored techniques like smoking and roasting to retain more of the food’s nutritional value and flavor. It results in a far better product that we think your pup will appreciate. And if you’re lucky, they’ll share.

Other bully stick brands may be too wide or narrow for the holder to work properly. What is the Bow Wow Buddy made out of? The Bow Wow Buddy is made in the USA with durable nylon that is BPA-free. Is the Bow Wow Buddy a chew toy? The Bow Wow Buddy is a safety device, not a toy. Promptly remove the device once your dog is done chewing their bully stick or other long-term chew. What is different about the redesigned Bow Wow Buddy? The redesigned orange Bow Wow Buddy has a flatter screw tip and an inner hole with three points of pressure to securely hold more chews. It is also dishwasher safe and Made in the USA.

title: Auris Blume HD Long Range Bluetooth 5.0 Music Receiver Hi-Fi Audio Adapter with Audiophile DAC & AptX HD for Home Stereo, AV Receiver or Amplifier
description: Creating audio solutions that simplify and enhance modern lifestyle. Founded in 2013, Auris Inc. is a team of engineers, audio geeks, and designers bound together with one sole purpose in mind: Creating audio solutions that simplify and enhance modern lifestyle. We believe in simplicity in design and deftness in function. In the age of digital streaming, our goal is to liberate music from the slavery of stationary listening and to give it the freedom modern wireless technology allows. bluMe HD | Premium Hi-Fi Bluetooth Music Receiver with 32-bit DAC and aptX HD Designed to connect traditional Hi-Fi stereo systems to the world of streaming audio and Internet radio, bluMe HD instantly breathes new life into your decades-old stereo equipment. Featuring an audiophile grade DAC, high-end audio codecs - aptX HD / aptX LL / aptX / AAC and wireless range to 100+ feet, bluMe HD is a true high fidelity premium Bluetooth Music Receiver that streams the highest quality audio wirelessly from your phone, tablet or computer to any music system or powered speakers. Makes any audio system wireless. Easy setup, connects in seconds. No App or wireless router network required. High fidelity Qualcomm aptX HD, aptX Low Latency, aptX and AAC decoders. Audiophile grade 384kHz / 32bit DAC for superior upsampled playback. High gain antenna for long range streaming up to 30m (100 feet). Featuring digital and analog output options. Connects to any audio system with RCA or optical inputs. Seamlessly works with all your apps, music, and devices. Tidal, Spotify, Pandora - all your favorite streaming apps play instantly. OVERVIEW | Highlights       Make Any Stereo System Wireless The advent of digital music has transformed the way we listen to music today. bluMeHD has been designed to connect your aging amplifier, a long-forgotten receiver or powered speakers to the ever expanding world of streaming audio and Internet radio. The bluMe HD Hi-Fi Bluetooth Music Receiver allows you to seamlessly stream stunning wireless music from your smart device to any stereo music system, making your favorite components sounding better than the day you brought them home. Unlimited Streaming bluMe HD can play any audio source a Bluetooth enabled device can access, opening up a virtually unlimited universe of music to enjoy through your Hi-Fi audio system. So you’re always in control not just of the music that’s stored on your device but also access premium high-res music services like Tidal, Spotify Qobuz and Pandora, internet radio stations, podcasts and even music libraries connected to a wireless home network...all instantly, wirelessly in Hi-Fi quality. Sounds Better Than Wired Vast majority of us tend to hard wire our smart devices to an audio system by either using a dock that pulls analog out of the device or by hooking up to the headphone output jack. In both cases the digital signal is processed by cheap low fidelity DAC used in all smart devices. With bluMe HD the digital signal is processed by its high-end DAC and high-definition audio decoders. No wonder bluMe HD sounds better than wired hookups! FEATURES | Benefits In Detail       Advanced Wireless Technology Featuring the best in class Bluetooth 5.0 technology and Qualcomm CSR8675 Bluetooth audio chip which is a premium low-power solution designed to deliver high quality wireless audio performance, bluMe HD ensures a stable and superior Bluetooth audio experience. High Quality Bluetooth Codecs With state-of-the-art Qualcomm aptX HD, bluMe HD can easily support 24-bit streaming directly from your phone or tablet, resulting in a ‘better-than-CD’ listening experience. Also, with support for high quality audio codecs like aptX Low Latency, aptX and AAC, bluMe HD provides an enhanced wireless listening experience for all your music via Bluetooth. Premium Hi-Fi DAC Equipped with the best in class true Hi-Fi 384kHz/32bit upsampling audiophile DAC - PCM5102A by TI that sports a high SNR of 112dB and is well regarded for its impressive low noise and low distortion characteristics. In short, this means that the sound you hear is crystal clear, rich and retains a wonderfully full dynamic range.       Enhanced Wireless Range Employs special circuitry and a precision-tuned external high gain antenna ensuring consistent, strong and glitch-free performance for 30 meters (100 feet), providing much more versatility than other Bluetooth receivers. Digital and Analog Connectivity Connect with high-quality gold-plated RCA Analog outputs or Digital Optical (SPIDF) output for true high resolution sound through your sound system. Premium Finish Encased in premium anodized aluminum housing, the compact and lightweight bluMe HD is a premium product in every sense which completely blends while sitting next to even the costliest and most attractive home audio components. description: At ReadyWise Food, we lead the food industry when it comes to emergency preparedness. description: Product Description The Zacurate Pro Series 500DL fingertip pulse oximeter is manufactured according to the CE and FDA standards set for pulse oximeter designed for sports enthusiasts, pilots or anyone who wants to obtain their SpO2 (blood oxygen saturation levels) and PR (Pulse Rate) on the go. The LED display now faces the user so that the user can read it easily. We have upgraded internal hardware and software components of the pulse oximeter. For example: the pulse oximeter can now display SpO2 up to 100%! Taking a reading is easy, just clip it on to your finger and turn it on at the press of a button. The large LED display makes viewing the results a snap. Its small size makes it easy to carry around and a lanyard is also included for added convenience. Comes with 2 AAA batteries and a silicon cover to protect your pulse oximeter from dirt and damage. Zacurate is a registered trademark of USPTO. We will actively and aggressively pursue any parties who infringe on our intellectual property rights to the maximum extent allowed by the law. Beware of Imitation, Buy Original. Zacurate Pulse oximeter is designed in USA. This device is for Sports & Aviation use only and is not a medical device. Note: Low blood perfusion can affect accuracy of your readings. Warm your hands and fingers before taking your measurements by rubbing your hands together. Remember your pulse oximeter is measuring your SpO2 and PR based on your blood flow. If the blood flow in your finger drops below a certain level, the pulse oximeter will not be able to function. It usually takes 10 seconds to get a reading. Some people though may require a longer time for the pulse oximeter to optimize its sensitivity. You may have to wait about 30 seconds for the readings to stabilize. Keep your hand still while taking a reading - any movement can cause the device to reset its' reading. Nail polish and fake fingernails may cause false readings. If possible, switch to an unpolished nail or consider another application site. Manufacturer Contact Information Refer to website

title: Thermal Paste, SYY 2 Grams CPU Paste Thermal
description: Excellent Performance The SYY-157 compound is composed of carbon micro-particles which lead to an extremely high thermal conductivity. It can improve that heat generated from the CPU or GPU is dissipated quickly and efficiently, even suitable for overclocking. Superb in performance, SYY-157 ranks among the top thermal compound, thermal paste, or thermal grease in the market.   Optimised Packaging Saves Resources A sustainable use of resources is really important for us at Thus we updated the packaging of the SYY-157 to minimize it's CO2 Footprint.   Safe Application The computer can work better after using thermal paste. It does not contain any metallic particles, so electrical conductivity would not be an issue. Unlike silver and copper compounds, it can contact any electrical pins that would not damage any sort.       Easy to Apply SYY-157 Thermal Conductive Paste has perfect ductility, and is thicker than other brands, so it doesn't flow everywhere, and comes with an application kit, making it easy to use even for beginners. Excellent Performance & Long-Lasting SYY-157 Thermal Paste has proven to have excellent efficacy and has been ranked in the top three of several non-sponsored influencers' thermal paste reviews. Lasts up to 5 years. Safe to Use SYY-157 Thermal Paste is made of silicon base and does not contain metal, so you can use it without worrying that it will conduct electricity or damage your computer.   Instruction for use SYY Thermal Paste was made by high quality materials to get better thermal conductivity, and there is an exclusive design that it is a little thicker while using, to avoid it flowing to the hardware around the cpu. If it is your first time to use thermal paste: Clean the surface of CPU and heat sink with cleaning wipes.Select the right size protective plate from the included kit and place it on the CPU.Apply an appropriate amount of thermal grease on the CPU.Use the included spatula to apply the thermal paste evenly to the CPU.You can also use the included scraper to apply it, or use it as a baffle to prevent the thermal paste from spreading outside the CPU.For maximum efficacy, please leave it for at least 15 minutes before installing heat sink.

description: Clear Incandescent Replacement Bulbs Specifications: 2.5 Volt170 mA0.425 Watts How do I know if these are the correct replacement bulbs I require?         Tip #1 Voltage & amperage are essential to take into consideration as you search for replacement bulbs. Tip #2 Double-check the white tag near the male plug of the light set. Tip #3 The tag should state something similar to the following "Use only 2.5V replacement lamps" and lower on the tag usually it will mention 0.34A or a similarly formatted number with "A" (representing Amperage) next to it. Tip #4 It is the amperage or milliamperage that control the brightness of the bulb. Voltage and amperage are essential to take into consideration as you search for replacement bulbs.

title: LMNT Zero Sugar Electrolytes - Citrus Salt | Drink Mix | 30-Count
description: BORN FROM A NEED, BACKED BY SCIENCE, AND BUILT FOR YOU. LMNT was born from a need. The hard truth is that available electrolyte products are high in sugar and woefully lacking in actual electrolytes. Based on the latest nutritional science, getting adequate electrolytes through these products equates to over 100 grams of added sugar per day. We don’t think anyone needs this amount of sugar. LMNT is formulated with everything you need and nothing you don’t. WHY LMNT? Healthy alternative to sugary sports drinks Support energy levels, endurance, and recovery Science-backed electrolyte ratio No sugar, no dodgy ingredients, no fillers, no junk Easy grab-and-go packaging   MORE OF THE GOOD STUFF There is a robust body of scientific literature that shows we have underestimated our electrolyte needs for decades, especially if you live an active, low-carb, or ketogenic lifestyle. Yet, popular electrolyte drinks on the market today still have low amounts of electrolytes and include a ton of sugar. LMNT gives you more electrolytes in the perfect ratio. 1,000 mg SODIUM200 mg POTASSIUM60 mg MAGNESIUM Key Ingredients: Salt (Sodium Chloride), Citric Acid, Magnesium Malate, Potassium Chloride, Natural Flavors, Stevia Leaf Extract   WITHOUT THE DODGY STUFF What we DON'T consume is just as important as what we DO consume. The research is clear - sugar, gluten, dodgy ingredients, and other irritants found in popular electrolyte drinks come at the expense of our health. No SugarNo GlutenNo Dodgy IngredientsNo Fillers Approximately 7-10% of the world's population suffers from sodium sensitivity. For those individuals, or those with fluid retention issues on the whole, additional sodium is generally not recommended, and our product is therefore not likely to be a good fit. However, approximately 90-93% of the world's population experiences no rise or only a modest, temporary increase in blood pressure. Those that try it tend to report the effects of higher-sodium electrolyte supplementation as "very positive," overall. If you have any medical conditions which necessitate the consumption of a low-sodium diet, using a high-dose electrolyte supplement is not recommended. If you experience adverse symptoms or effects such as nausea, bloating, stomach pains, diarrhea or vomiting when trying LMNT, cease use of the product. Note the quantity of water you use to dilute LMNT, the timeframe for drinking it (e.g. sipping it over the course of an hour vs. chugging it in a few mins), and any other new activities or dietary tinkering might have an impact on your experience of LMNT. title: Doctor's Best Vitamin D3 5,000 IU for Healthy Bones, Teeth, Heart and Immune Support, Non-GMO, Gluten-Free, Soy Free, 360 Count (Pack of 1)
description: Vitamin d from dietary intake or sun exposure requires two activation steps in the body. The first activation occurs in the liver, while the second activation occurs in the kidneys, allowing for regulation of calcium metabolism. However, vitamin d receptors are present throughout the body, in tissue such as the skin, cartilage, heart, prostate, bones and intestines. Thus, the second activation step also takes place in local tissues. Recent discoveries have highlighted the important modulatory effects of vitamin d on various cells of the immune system.vitamin d enhances and regulates immune function. It is known that various cells of the immune system, such as t lymphocytes and antigen presenting cells, express the vitamin d receptor on their surface when activated. Recently, it has been found that treatment of these immune cells with vitamin d influences their expression of cytokines, which are chemical messengers of the immune system. The immune modulating effects of vitamin d extend to monocytes and dendritic cells of the immune system as well. Dendritic cells are important antigen-processing cells of the immune system that function to initiate the immune response. Vitamin d may prevent overactivity of the immune response and keep the immune system in a normal healthy state of vigilance.vitamin d supports optimal cardiovascular function. Research has uncovered the role vitamin d plays in supporting cardiac function. Heart myocytes (cells) express the vitamin d receptor, as do smooth muscle cells of blood vessels. The benefits of vitamin d on the heart are potentially far-reaching. Studies on mice heart cells have shown that vitamin d administration impacts their growth and proliferation. In these cells, vitamin d inhibited the release of a protein that could be detrimental to the function of these cells, displaying cardioprotective properties. It has also been shown that vitamin d has a modulatory effect on heart rhythm.

description: Dusk to Dawn Auto On/Off Featuring advanced photocell sensors, these light sensing bulbs are carefree to use. All you need to do is keep the power switch on and let them be. Can these bulbs be used in outdoor fixtures with frosted glass? Most of the light bulbs which has a sensing eye/hole on the body cannot use in the canister light fixture because such enclosed light fixture completely blocks the sensor to sense the sunlight. People are asleep and require less light after an Outdoor Dusk to Dawn sensor light working for 6 hours. title: FiiO BTR3K Receiver Amplifier Bluetooth Headphone Amp High Resolution Support aptX HD/aptX LL/LDAC for Car Audio/Home TV/Speaker/Smartphones/PC (3.5mm/2.5mm Output)
description: Selling points summary 1. Balanced and SE output: Truly balanced design with better measurements and better actual sound. 2. Strong decoding: Flagship Qualcomm CSR8675. 3. Lossless support: Bluetooth 5.0，supports LDAC/aptX HD and other lossless formats. 4. Improved measurements: 2x high-performance AK4377A DACs 5. Precise signal reproduction: dual 22.5792M/24.576M crystal design. 6. Double-sided 2.5D glass:aluminum alloy body + double-sided glass. 7.Helps with computer audio: Driverless, plug-and-play USB DAC. 8.RGB light indicator: quickly identifies Bluetooth format. 9.Precise volume control: Volume control independent from device 10. Extended functionality from app: channel balance, audio filters, EQ Parameters BT Version:BT5.0 3.5mm Headphone Output:25mW@32Ω 2.5mm Balanced Output:78mW@32Ω USB DAC: AK4377A*2 USB DAC Sample Rate:48K/16bit Noise floor(Balanced out): 2uV Phase shift(Balanced out):0.03deg(10KHz) SNR(A-weight): 122   Now with balanced and SE output Buidling off the what made the BTR3 so good, the BTR3K implements balanced output. It is a truly balanced design, with a DAC and amplifier carefully paired for the left and right channels each, for the purest sound possible.   Robust, full-bodied sound, High performance AK4377A DACs With two high-performance AK4377A DACs, the power output has increased by 50% compared to the AK4376 used in the BTR3K as well as greatly improved measurements and actual sound. Distortion -107dB | S/N Ratio 122dB | Output power balanced 78mW | Output power SE 25mW   Qualcomm CSR8675 Flagship-level Bluetooth abilities The Qualcomm CSR8675 Bluetooth chip used in the BTR3K is a premium low-power solution designed for enhanced audio applications, with a 120 MHz DSP, support for 24-bit transmission and processing as well as abilities to decode multiple lossless Bluetooth codecs. Support for the AAC/SBC/aptX/aptX LL/aptX HD/LDAC audio formats ensures that you’ll get the best sound quality possible from the BTR3K.   Independent dual crystal oscillators for accurate audio reproduction The dual crystal oscillator system in the BTR5 also comes to the BTR3K! The 22.5792M/24.576 MHz dual crystal oscillators mean that during Bluetooth and USB decoding, the BTR3K can more accurately reproduce audio signals under various sampling rates – due to greatly reduced jitter and greatly increased audio stability.   Intelligently puts your music at your fingertips When your device is connected to the BTR3K and is using the FiiO Music app to play music, the BTR3K can be remotely controlled with the following functions: 1、Channel balance 2、Switch between 4 kinds of audio filters 3、10-band professional EQ (equalizer)*EQ invalid in LDAC codec   Technical support for BTR3K 1.How to connect the BTR3K to new devices? Pairing mode With blue and red lights flashing alternately, it means it is in pairing mode. Note that the first time you turn on th power or clear the pairing information, the BTR3K will automatically enter the pairing mode. How to connect to new devices 1.Ensure the BTR3K is in pairing mode: long press the play/pause button for 5s to enter pairing mode with blue and red indicator lights flashing alternatively. 2.Enter Bluetooth Settings on your phone, choosing the BTR3K to complete the connection. 2.Why does the volume of the mobile phone not change when the BTR3K adjusts the volume? 1.There is a memory function within the BTR3K so that it can automatically adjust the volume. 2. We have deliberately designed the volume adjustment of the BTR3K out of sync with the mobile phone which makes it possible to adjust the volume in a more precise level and avoid many problems. What the mobile phone can adjust is the the volume of the Bluetooth codec. If its volume is too small, the dynamic effect would be affected. While the BTR3K controls the volume of decoding and amplification which can decrease the loss of the sound quality. Therefore, it is recommended to adjust the volume of the phone to the maximum, and control the volume by the BTR3K. 3.Does the BTR3K support in-line remote and the microphone function？ In-line remote The BTR3K supports the CTIA standard for line control as well as line microphone. But the headsets with OMTP protocol only support normal listening. Microphone recording Android-based cellphones can normally use WeChat,Wechat calls, QQ voice and QQ calls. The phone microphone is used when taking videos, using QQ voices and Wechat voice. It depends on different systems of mobile phones. iOS system only supports WeChat voice, calls and QQ calls with the microphone of BTR3K. If taking a video, the phone mircophone is used. 4.EQ is invalid under BTR3K's LDAC. Is it a hardware defect or a software problem? Notices: Third-party music apps could also use the EQ adjustment if it is the function of BTR3K. If it indicates that the EQ is invalid, you can turn on the EQ switch and reboot the BTR3K to activate the EQ function. EQ invalid in LDAC codec It is not a hardware defect. Since the audio processing of LDAC is more special than other Bluetooth formats, we are still doing related debugging, and striving to achieve the same effect as other Bluetooth formats, but it will take a certain amount of time.
